Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,﻿快来  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.16,0:01:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会爱上魔法小屋的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll love the Magic Shack
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证可以让你目瞪口呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guarantee you'll be astounded and amazed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都跟你说过了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told ya, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不去看什么骗人的魔法表演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't going to no phony hocus-pocus show
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是专攻科学的松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a science squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.17,0:01:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不相信魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in magic
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可大家命中都需要一丢丢魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But everyone needs a widdle magic in their "wives"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.93,0:01:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  去就去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我连一丢丢都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not gonna wike it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  准备好目瞪口呆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, prepare to be astonished and stupefied
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来观赏神秘魔法  表演者就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by the mysterious magic of
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大法师豪迪尼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Great Howdini
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪家伙  他怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Howdini" do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪光纸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flash paper
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都老掉牙的魔术了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oldest trick in the book
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪家伙  他怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Howdini" do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牌都用胶水粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cards are glued together
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪家伙  他怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Howdini" do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用镜子和烟雾投影出来的障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's doing it all with smoke and mirrors
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪家伙  他怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Howdini" do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是全能的豪迪尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the all-powerful Howdini
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,T恤衫可以前往大堂购买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,T-shirts can be purchased in the lobby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,演完魔法之后
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想不出任何有逻辑的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't come up with any logical explanation
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来说明他怎么表演的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for how he did that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就是违反了科学原理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It goes against science
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法是没法解释的  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't explain magic, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪迪尼先生  可以给我签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Howdini, can I have an autograph?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd be delighted
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也会表演魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do a magic trick too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,业余
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amateur
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿着我的魔法棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold my wand
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以签在我的背上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you sign my back?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就签  我的小不点朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, my little friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的笔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your pen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来捡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吊威亚 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wires?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全息投影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holograms?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,催眠术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hypnosis?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪啊  魔法本来就不合逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sandy, magic isn't logical
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya later
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得回家喂小蜗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta go home and feed Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, see ya
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在魔法小屋那边吃太多爆米花了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too much Magic Shack popcorn
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都跟你说多少遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说过不要做的事情不要做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not to do what I told you not to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:40.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(576,330)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说过不要做了  你却又不听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you not to, but you did not listen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非做跟你说过不要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you did the thing that I told you not to do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得像我没跟你说过不要做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as if I never told you not to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听不见  我在喷杀虫剂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't hear you, spraying bugs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gare-bear
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天过得好充实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看了大法师豪迪尼演了特神的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw Howdini the Great do amazing things
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪却不相信魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Sandy didn't believe in magic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过豪迪尼让她漂浮在舞台上空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Howdini made her float up on stage
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得珊迪现在都动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now she's not so sure of herself
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你趁我不在重新装修了客厅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, did you redecorate the living room while I was out?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不废话了  来喂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll quit my jabbering and feed you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腐烂的植物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rotting vegetation
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最爱的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your favorite flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon appetit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,892)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛吃台球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating billiard balls?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过更严重的问题应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I guess the bigger question is
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干嘛要喂你吃台球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why did I feed you billiard balls?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,助步器老头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Walker?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where's Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是小蜗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你是小蜗  那就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're Gary, then tell me something
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有真正的小蜗才知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only the real Gary would know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我睡觉还真会打嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do belch in my sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, it is you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我好像出现幻觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I think I'm seeing things
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在豪迪尼的魔法表演肯定是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at Howdini's magic show
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就去看急诊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the emergency room right now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:38.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,872)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到你的病情所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see your trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的身体里有一根魔法棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a magic wand inside you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而你又频繁打嗝  就触发了它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And your hiccups are setting it off
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是把豪迪尼的魔法棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have mixed up Howdini's wand
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,误认成我的签字笔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my autograph pen
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.81,0:07:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我伸手进去  帮你掏出魔法棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let me just dig in there and get that wand for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要不然就治好你的打嗝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if we just cure your hiccups instead?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你打点水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some water
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll fix it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doc
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hiccups are gone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1088,512)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要医生  我需要珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need a doctor, I need a Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法棒就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's the wand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要分析一下那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to analyze that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看它怎么变的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see how it makes magic
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇一摇就能掉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll come loose if I give it a good shake
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.53,0:07:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.94,0:07:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.36,0:07:48.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forgot to say
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇一下就会触发魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The shaking is what triggers the magic
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种能施魔法的玩意一定得轻拿轻放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta handle this enchanted doohickey
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,real delicate-like
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, dang
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the magician
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  他见到我们的样子好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, does he look happy to see us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么发现我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you find us?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道是用心灵感应发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With your telepathic powers?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的魔法棒有定位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wand has GPS
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可悲的笔还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your pathetic pen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把魔法棒还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give me back my wand
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经玩够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've had your fun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是问题所在  豪弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the problem, Howdooya
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的魔法棒卡在我朋友身体里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your wand is stuck in my friend here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇都摇不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we can't shake it out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就把它弄出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算要撕碎他也在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even If I have to tear him apart
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了  魔法棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to save you, Wanda
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就感觉这家伙疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling this guy was nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要像切牌一样切了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll cut you like a deck of cards
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许伤害我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是我的魔法棒  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my magic wand, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dagnabbit
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃我一魔法  吸血鬼德古拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat magic, Dracula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想戴耳环
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted earrings
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞吧  我的蛤蜊们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fly, my clammies
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这简直是异想天开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a stretch of the imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1192,920)}拉
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还是相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm a believer
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得处理一两件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta take care of a couple of things
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到要怎么取出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just figured out how to get
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身体里的魔法棒了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the magic wand out of you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是科学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Science
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大泡弹汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fizz Bomb Soda
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打个大爆嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Burp Explosion
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇动汽水  就会释放出二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The agitation of the soda releases carbon dioxide
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把魔法棒逼出你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which will force the wand out of your body
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下再也不往身上的洞里放东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll teach me not to put stuff in my pores
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.01,标准-Chi,,0,500,0,,豪弟弟  我会把你变回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,500,0,,Alright, Howdooya, I'll turn you back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,500,0,,但条件是你给我安分点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,500,0,,but only if you play nice
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从前一直不相信科学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never believed in science
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直到我看到了那套汽水变气球的戏法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I saw that soda and balloon trick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙  珊迪怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"How-Sandy" do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我八年级科学课就学会那套戏法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I learned that trick in 8th grade science class
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能再多给我介绍下这个科学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me more about this "science"?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来我实验室一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in to my lab
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你展示一些实验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you some experiments
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证惊到你山羊胡都在转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that'll make your goatee spin
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.83,0:11:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都有科学了  还要什么魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs magic when you have science
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.18,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,过度迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:51.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.47,0:11:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,﻿啊  我们回到了蟹老板的海军生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, here we are, back in Mr. Krabs' old navy days
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,664)}海军生涯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是年轻时的蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here is the young Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,践行着海军的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,exercising the Navy's honor
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,勇气  与奉献精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,courage, and commitment
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而践行方式是给甲板拖地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by swabbing the deck
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  拖地的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful there, swabbie
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从梯子底下走过去会倒霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's bad luck to walk under a ladder
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤其是在十三号星期五这天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially on Friday the 13th
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不迷那个破信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't stupor-stitious
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just watch me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.17,0:12:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全是无稽之谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All balderdash
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And looky here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬过了只黑蜗牛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A black snail just crossed me path
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥都没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zilch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在玩命  水手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're tempting fate, sailor
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么无脑迷信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's another stupid-stition?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打碎镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breaking a mirror
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.20,0:13:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清晨天空红  水手敲警钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:13:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Red sky in morning, sailor take warning
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told ya so
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十三号星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friday the 13th
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是十三号星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's Friday the 13th
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天最好小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I best be careful today
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁朝下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horseshoe facing down
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.99,0:13:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厄运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad luck
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's starting
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.05,0:13:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到别针不去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See a pin, let it lay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好运全部都不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all good luck will pass away
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(488,412)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋里打伞  厄运泛滥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Umbrella open inside, bad luck is on the tide
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.02,0:14:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那水管往我脑袋滴了我一早上的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That pipe's been dripping on my head all morning
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又能怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就当免费洗了个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just enjoy the free shower
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞋子放桌上  运气不稳当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shoes on the table, your luck be unstable
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.71,0:14:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.89,0:14:56.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋里吹口哨  运气都跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:56.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An indoor whistle brings luck's dismissal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是在闹什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the commotion in the ocean?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是十三号星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Friday the 13th
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.95,0:15:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板一年比一年迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Mr. Krabs gets more superstitious every year
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会是先迈左脚进蟹堡王的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't enter me restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your left foot, did ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口袋里有水煮蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any boiled eggs in your pockets?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有墓地里的石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stones from a cemetery?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有干制鱼首级吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shrunken fish heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.80,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 干制首级：将战争中砍下的头\N干缩当作战利品保存，有时用于祭祀 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  没有违禁品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're clean
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.87,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 此为前述的干制首级 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你要不是厄运缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pal, if it weren't for bad luck
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本连运气都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd have no luck at all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:54.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(458,800)}头号老板
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的早茶马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your morning cup of tea, coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用小刀搅拌  就是挑争端
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stir with a knife, you'll stir up strife
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪眼出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The evil eye
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人升天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone will die
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那领带哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get that tie?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个旧领带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This old tie?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之前是我曾曾爷爷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It belonged to my great-great grandfather
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死人领带  末日要来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dead man's tie, the end is nigh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead yet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾曾爷爷好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Great-Great Grandpa
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领带还你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your tie back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.72,0:16:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵可以活两百年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponges can live up to 200 years
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹要是别老想那个破迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe Krabs would have time to fix this leaky pipe
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.00,0:16:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计就有空来修这个漏水的水管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if he didn't obsess over dumb superstitions
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想把事办成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want something done
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then do it yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静点  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要玩命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tempt fate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,熬过今天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just make it through the day
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走后门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The back door
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我办公室没后门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no back door to my office
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也是厄运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that also bad luck?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.80,0:17:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是厄运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you bad luck?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是厄运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I bad luck?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们两个凑在一起就是厄运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we both bad luck together?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, poo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚对我切什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you just "poo" me?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能把自己反锁在办公室里一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't stay locked up in your office forever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王还需要经营呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab needs managing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多半是太过大惊小怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm probably getting all worked up over nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来一切安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like the coast is clear
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心那个水坑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out for that puddle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out for wha
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladder?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一只黑蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another black snail?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打翻的盐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spilled salt?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还有呼吸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he breathing?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't tell
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他冒了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's his breath
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's breathing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碎镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Broken mirror?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's happening again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在海军生涯里没出过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't happen in me old navy days
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一只小妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a leprechaun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是小妖粗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a lepre-can't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反向版的小妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A reverse leprechaun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们是厄运的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're bad luck personified
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you so
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们早上倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bottom of the morning to ya
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Smatter?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被蜗牛咬到舌头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snail got your tongues?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.78,0:18:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛光站那  跟木头做的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are ye just standing there like you're made of wood?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都是木头做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all made of wood
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓得我呆若木鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shiver me timbers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都变木头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all timbers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要用幸运抵消厄运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to counteract the bad luck with some good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would be great if we could find some
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敲木头会有好运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock on wood
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家敲木头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone knock on wood
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我头快裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me splittin' cranium
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A rainbow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩虹尽头有装满黄金的罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are pots of gold at the end of rainbows
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到黄金我就能发财了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could be rich with all that gold
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到黄金我就能辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could quit my job with all that gold
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到黄金就能用它在地上写我名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could spell my name out on the floor with all that gold
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.23,0:20:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.87,0:20:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nix
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰那个罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay away from that pot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四叶草
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four-leaf clovers?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兔脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rabbits' feet?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the gold?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马蹄铁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horseshoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许愿骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishbones?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些都是幸运符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are all lucky charms
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸运蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A lucky cake
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜猜谁现在可以许愿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And guess who gets to make a wish now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那些东西放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put those things back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都不准碰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mustn't touch them
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here ya go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.13,0:20:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.87,0:20:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我突然感觉很幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, I'm feeling lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.41,0:20:41.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.36,0:20:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cease
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.53,0:21:00.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小妖粗变成了小妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:00.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lepre-can't just turned into a lepre-can
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准确来说是变回才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turned back into, to be precise
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.82,0:21:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几十年前  有个老海巫婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Twas decades ago that an old sea witch
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我变成了小妖粗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,turned me into a lepre-can't
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过多亏了你们  我又复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But thanks to you, I'm restored
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.07,0:21:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能变回带来幸运的绿模样  太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Tis grand to be me old green, good-luck self again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank thee, gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从头到脚  恢复肉身多完好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Return to meats from your heads to your feets
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又伸缩自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm porous again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我没记错那些上古传说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now if I remember the old legends correctly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.27,0:21:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是抓到小妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you catch a leprechaun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小妖精就得把他那罐黄金送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's got to give you his pot of gold
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会相信那通废话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't believe all that malarkey, do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天信了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've believed a lot today
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先抓到我再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta catch me first
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在找一罐黄金吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking for a pot of gold?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.35,0:22:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我最喜欢彩虹的什么特点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know the one thing I love most about rainbows?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.06,0:22:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.75,0:22:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩虹很漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're pretty?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩虹不会永存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't last forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.94,0:22:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Black snail
